  - m_Id: 28388352843794
    m_Localized: "<align=center><b>Welcome Champ!</b></align>\n\nBuilding games is
      a complex endeavor that requires input from many sources, testing, and iteration
      to create the best user experience. The Game you are playing is a beta version
      that is under development and might contain bugs, errors and missing features
      that can impact your experience. \n\nThe game includes optional web3 elements
      that require you to use and interact with 3rd party apps such as crypto wallets,
      dex platforms and nft marketplaces. All these features are here to enhance
      your gameplay but are completely optional and don't impact core gameplay.\n\nOur
      goal is to build the game for the players - together with the players. If you
      wish to take more active role please join us at beta.cosmicchamps.com.\n\nDuring
      the development period we might occasionally delete the user accounts and data
      associated with them and no progress will be preserved for the official public
      release of the game.\n\nEverything you see in the game is subject to change."
    m_Metadata:
